  "titles": "Centurion in Terminator Armour",
  "lore": "Centurions make up the bulk of Legion officers. When facing heavy resistance, many centurions will march to war clad in Terminator armour, leading their subordinates into the thickest fighting. Line centurions fight in the vanguard of Legion forces, the superior durability and protection afforded by Terminator suits greatly increasing the survivability of such a perilous duty, as well as providing a platform for additional fi repower. Some of the greatest victories of the Great Crusade were won by a bold centurion storming a breached fortress clad in ornamented Terminator plate.",
